SCHABARUM, PETE; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- SUITS; APPEALS; LEGAL COSTS; RACIAL 
DISCRIMINATION; HISPANICS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; MISUSE OF PUBLIC FUNDS; 
SECRECY; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- POLITICS 
