<P>
Telecredit Inc.: The Los Angeles business services company, which provides 
credit card processing services to banks, credit unions and savings 
institutions, said net income for the year rose 15% to a record $28.5 million, 
while revenue increased 5% to a record $167.6 million. The firm said the 
results reflect a 17% after-tax return on revenue and a 33% after-tax return on 
average stockholders' equity. 
