WAGES AND SALARIES; LIFESTYLES; QUALITY OF LIFE; EAST GERMANY -- INDUSTRY; 
EMPLOYMENT -- EAST GERMANY; EAST GERMANY -- CURRENCY; EMOTIONS 
</P>
