<TEXT>
<P>
Gov. Garrey E. Carruthers has rejected a writer's request that Billy the Kid be 
pardoned for his role in the 1878 shooting death of Sheriff William Brady. 
</P>
<P>
A letter is being prepared telling Las Cruces author Opal Lee Priestley of the 
